  "detailed_description": "<strong>Kiting Mechanics</strong> was built by an army of two botlane connoisseurs who wanted to have a tool to get in the groove of <strong>kiting</strong> and <strong>dodging skillshots</strong> before their games.<br>We made sure every aspect of the game feels and performs the same as the real deal, so training here means  getting good out there.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kite</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/1e80dbf4b3db74e53e8e72aa80a433be.poster.avif?t=1679308744\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/1e80dbf4b3db74e53e8e72aa80a433be.webm?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/1e80dbf4b3db74e53e8e72aa80a433be.mp4?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Develop reliable kiting skills by practicing in tough situations that will make teamfighting feel like a walk in the park.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dodge</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/86c7559f5979ccb47621dc5df914e1a3.poster.avif?t=1679308744\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/86c7559f5979ccb47621dc5df914e1a3.webm?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/86c7559f5979ccb47621dc5df914e1a3.mp4?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Build some strong anticipation and make sidestepping second nature.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Custom Ping</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/72a5fb99b98ff550e5125f301f232c33.poster.avif?t=1679308744\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/72a5fb99b98ff550e5125f301f232c33.webm?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/72a5fb99b98ff550e5125f301f232c33.mp4?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>To make sure you didn't get used to 0 ping latency, we built an artifical ping system. This way you can train with the same ping you typically get in real games.<br><br>In Kiting Mechanics you will roam around a vast map where you must fight hordes of mobs to get to the next round. Along the way you will pick up some juicy <strong>perks</strong> to spice up your run and get as far as possible in the ranking.<br><br><br><i>Your micro will thank you.</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Kiting Mechanics</strong> was built by an army of two botlane connoisseurs who wanted to have a tool to get in the groove of <strong>kiting</strong> and <strong>dodging skillshots</strong> before their games.<br>We made sure every aspect of the game feels and performs the same as the real deal, so training here means  getting good out there.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kite</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/1e80dbf4b3db74e53e8e72aa80a433be.poster.avif?t=1679308744\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/1e80dbf4b3db74e53e8e72aa80a433be.webm?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/1e80dbf4b3db74e53e8e72aa80a433be.mp4?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Develop reliable kiting skills by practicing in tough situations that will make teamfighting feel like a walk in the park.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dodge</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/86c7559f5979ccb47621dc5df914e1a3.poster.avif?t=1679308744\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/86c7559f5979ccb47621dc5df914e1a3.webm?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/86c7559f5979ccb47621dc5df914e1a3.mp4?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Build some strong anticipation and make sidestepping second nature.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Custom Ping</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/72a5fb99b98ff550e5125f301f232c33.poster.avif?t=1679308744\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/72a5fb99b98ff550e5125f301f232c33.webm?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289930/extras/72a5fb99b98ff550e5125f301f232c33.mp4?t=1679308744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>To make sure you didn't get used to 0 ping latency, we built an artifical ping system. This way you can train with the same ping you typically get in real games.<br><br>In Kiting Mechanics you will roam around a vast map where you must fight hordes of mobs to get to the next round. Along the way you will pick up some juicy <strong>perks</strong> to spice up your run and get as far as possible in the ranking.<br><br><br><i>Your micro will thank you.</i>",
